Package: mopt
Type: Package
Title: Parallel Derivative-free Moment Estimation
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-02-14
Author: Ran Gu [ctb],
    Thibaut Lamadon [ctb,cre],
    Florian Oswald [ctb]
Maintainer: Thibaut Lamadon <thibaut.lamadon@gmail.com>,
    Florian Oswald <florian.oswald@gmail.com>
Description: mopt is a suite of derivative-free MCMC optimization algorithms
    that can be used to find the maximum of an objective function. The package
    is designed with a particular focus on cases where this objective function
    is composed of moment conditions. This includes standard GMM as well as
    simulated method of moments or indeed any other moment-like estimation.
License: MIT
